title: O'Neill - TECHNOBUTTER
description: TechnoButter: O'Neill's exclusive TechnoButter Neoprene boasts a 20% lighter formula with a 30% less water absorption and quick dry properties that make this the most technical and buttery neoprene on the market. Available in the O'Neill Psychofreak, Psycho 3 and Psycho 1.
